{"tid":1711661,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"尋求共識：先歸英 後商議","createTime":"2019-11-12T12:13:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T14:38:05.000Z","uid":215950,"like":327,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"9432bbda2e0ea60ad3233bc58510af2c310ac983","tid":1711661,"uid":215950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T12:13:36.000Z","msg":"我明白抗爭有好多種選項，但如果抗爭者之間都未有共識既話，我地會更加難勝利。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">先歸英</span><br />\n係因為中英聯合聲明已經失效，根據法律同國際慣例，香港係名正言順返回聲明前既狀態，即係回歸英國統治。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">後商議</span><br />\n至於要唔要獨立，我地唔需要同林鄭或者中國大陸傾，我地應該係同英國政府傾，呢啲可以等回歸英國之後慢慢做。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">總結</span><br />\n名正言順，合法合理，全體共識：先歸英，後商議。<br />\n<br />\n大家同唔同意？"},{"pid":"50dd8c119ac785fe97f764582ebd0ae3c531f370","tid":1711661,"uid":181778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T12:16:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b0c651575e6119a8f4456761ae525c72bc82415a","tid":1711661,"uid":215950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T12:19:03.000Z","msg":"推 1/10"},{"pid":"0df64ccad6d59a015915811f9cd47f1015cbccff","tid":1711661,"uid":215950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T12:35:41.000Z","msg":"推 2/10"},{"pid":"fce61e0c62bec9f34e5666ad700f80eefbe4f713","tid":1711661,"uid":263484,"like":1,"dislike":18,"score":-17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T12:36:47.000Z","msg":"歸咩丫<br />\n眾籌買個島好過"},{"pid":"29fc19600857f0fb3265fbec256ab9d84a1aefc0","tid":1711661,"uid":25019,"like":4,"dislike":20,"score":-16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T12:39:54.000Z","msg":"英國人起華為5g了<br />\n你估當年大英帝國？<br />\n要幫你6.9已經幫左啦"},{"pid":"6fe173e1f3cb30d7daaa020cd54f39b2204173c9","tid":1711661,"uid":136797,"like":6,"dislike":12,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T12:40:49.000Z","msg":"英國奶緊共點得閒理香港"},{"pid":"4d678fdaf3bc2df1e6fa861cea60997e6b1cdf67","tid":1711661,"uid":185045,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11